44:01.333 --> 44:03.708
[geraman rendah]

44:03.791 --> 44:05.541
[gemuruh]

44:07.708 --> 44:09.416
[teriakan bernada tinggi]

44:09.500 --> 44:11.625
-[Maximus] Sial, sial, sial, sial.
-[Thaddeus berteriak]

44:11.708 --> 44:15.166
-Tuanku! [berteriak]
-Aku menangkapmu!

44:15.250 --> 44:16.500
Ksatria Titus!

44:16.583 --> 44:18.541
[menggeram]

44:18.625 --> 44:20.416
[teriakan bernada tinggi]

44:20.500 --> 44:23.541
[berteriak]

44:25.291 --> 44:26.208
[menelan ludah dalam-dalam]

44:26.291 --> 44:28.250
Aku masuk! [teriak]

44:28.333 --> 44:31.541
-Aku menangkapmu!
-[berteriak]

44:31.625 --> 44:33.166
[Maximus mendengus]

44:33.250 --> 44:36.041
[teriakan] Kemenangan!

44:36.125 --> 44:39.291
[Maximus berteriak]

44:39.375 --> 44:42.666
[geraman rendah]

44:42.750 --> 44:44.500
[erangan]

44:46.333 --> 44:48.125
[teriakan bernada tinggi]

44:48.208 --> 44:51.083
[Thaddeus berteriak]

44:51.166 --> 44:53.416
[Gulper mengerang]

44:53.500 --> 44:55.708
[Thaddeus mengerang, merintih]

45:02.416 --> 45:03.958
[Maximus] Ah.

45:06.000 --> 45:07.666
-Kau menyelamatkanku!
-Hah.

45:07.750 --> 45:10.083
Kamu menyelamatkanku duluan.

45:14.958 --> 45:17.750
[musik kontemplatif diputar]

45:19.708 --> 45:21.250
[gonggongan]

45:28.666 --> 45:30.666
Hah. Oh.

45:33.791 --> 45:36.750
[musik suram dimainkan]

45:38.625 --> 45:41.333
[CX404 merintih]

45:45.583 --> 45:48.250
[CX404 mengendus]

45:48.333 --> 45:50.541
Apakah itu...?

45:50.625 --> 45:52.791
Kepala.

45:52.875 --> 45:54.458
[Thaddeus] Kepalanya?!

45:54.541 --> 45:56.750
Itu kepalanya! Ya!

45:56.833 --> 45:58.916
-Ya!
-[ups]

45:59.000 --> 46:00.416
Ya!

